title: El Domo del Dinero
overview: Two teams of extraordinary "ordinary" participants battle it out in a variety of challenges that range from physical to cognitive in order win big cash prizes inside the stunning Domo del Dinero. Viewers at home will follow their heroes closely and vote for them through social media. A daily live competition reality show where hectic physical, dexterous, knowledge-based, artistic and fun challenges come together in a high-energy television show for the whole family. Week after week, there will be one winning team and one team that will bear the elimination of a teammate. In the end, only two teams of five will remain to battle it out in the Grand Finale.
